detail.name: Zarbon
detail.effect: [On Play] Look at 5 cards from the top of your deck, then reveal up to 1 card that includes <Frieza> in its card name and add it to your hand. Place the rest at the bottom of your deck in a random order.

detail.name: ザーボン
detail.effect: [登場時]自分のデッキの上から5枚を見て、カード名に「フリーザ」を含むカード1枚までを公開し、手札に加える。残りをランダムにデッキの下に置く。
